    "cooking_instructions": [
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Preheat the grill to high</p><p>Top, tail and slice the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>on a diagonal</p><p>Deseed the <strong>pepper<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thick strips</p>",
            "order": 1,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-1.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>sliced courgette </strong>and <strong>pepper strips</strong> to a large baking tray<strong> </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>and pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray under the<strong> </strong>grill for 8-10 min until softened and charred \u2013 these are your <strong>grilled vegetables</strong></p>",
            "order": 2,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-2.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Whilst the vegetables are under the grill, slice the <strong>tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</span></strong> into wedges</p><p>Peel and chop the<strong> red onion<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> </strong>into wedges</p><p>Cut the <strong>halloumi</strong> into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> slices</p>",
            "order": 3,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-3.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>green tomato chutney</strong> with the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]<strong> </span>lemon</strong>,<strong> </strong>2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>in a small bowl \u2013 this is your <strong>green tomato dressing</strong></p><p>Cut the <strong>remaining lemon</strong> into wedges</p>",
            "order": 4,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-4.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>onion</strong> and <strong>tomato wedges</strong></p><p>Cook for 3-4 min or until starting to soften</p>",
            "order": 5,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-5.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Once the onion and tomato wedges are starting to soften, add the <strong>halloumi slices</strong></p><p>Cook for 1-2 min on each side or until golden</p>",
            "order": 6,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-6.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and shred roughly</p><p>Divide the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>between your serving plates</p>",
            "order": 7,
            "image": "/images/instructions/warm-halloumi-salad-with-green-tomato-dressing/step-7.jpg"
        },
        {
            "instruction": "<p>Top<strong> </strong>the<strong> shredded lettuce </strong>with the <strong>grilled vegetables </strong>and<strong> softened tomatoes </strong>and <strong>red onion wedges</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>golden halloumi slices </strong>over the vegetables</p><p>Drizzle everything with the <strong>green tomato dressing</strong> and garnish with the <strong>pumpkin seeds </strong>and a <strong>lemon wedge</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
            "order": 8
        }
    ],
